modules.description: Provides functions to open and close an SQLite database, and to execute queries returning results as a list of Yojson associations. Operates with SQLite database handles and Yojson data structures. Used to retrieve query results in a structured format for further processing or API responses.

Opens and manages SQLite databases with options for memory, mode, and concurrency control. Executes SQL statements and retrieves results as JSON arrays, supporting parameter binding. Works with custom binding and record types for structured data handling.
